{"tid":2047720,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國賣產#689兌美金 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-06-02T09:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T09:41:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"11eac2d302c54258f5893e2cbd290e66bb6dbe1a","tid":2047720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:41:08.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200602/20928902/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200602%2F20928902%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=effe688d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200602%2F20928902%2F&h=b683d547\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200602/20928902/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國賣產#689兌美金 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200602/large/1591006595_2dec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200602%2Flarge%2F1591006595_2dec.jpg&h=5f7f46e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊局長支笛，由見記者時一直左手捂住自己左邊屁股的張司長接嘴，吹脹！29%自稱非民主派人士，接受香港民研調查，竟然反對国安法。成何體統！<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n擔心唔知幾時被美國杏家橙的，有離晒罩、痛濕底褲的777、司局長兩會議員與黑警，天網不漏，佔港人29%啱條數。再也捂不住（張司長囑家人急賣產，689兌美金），老海鮮效應，七月十四鬼門關，提早開。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}